name: Isekai madness: I haven't died but I still got summoned to another world!???
name_original: Isekai madness: I haven't died but I still got summoned to another world!???
description:
A girl named Phoebe has summoned 2 mysterious women in order to defeat the Demon King.

Can they actually defeat their enemies? Or has Phoebe made a terrible mistake?
